    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>眠れないのかい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Can't sleep?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、うん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, no...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277708</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう言えば、
僕の話を聞きたいって
言ってたよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It looks like there's something
you wish to tell me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……だった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Erm...it's just...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしたち、
ダオスに襲われたんです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos tried to attack us earlier.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスに？
また時空を越えて……
いや、そんなまさか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos, you say!? Could he have
travelled through time again...?
No, that's impossible...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それにしても、どうして
ダオスに襲われるんだ。
君たちみたいな子どもが</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why would Dhaos attack you?
You look just like regular kids.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278152</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔王が人間襲うのに
理由なんてねんだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Demon King is known for attacking
innocent people. So nothing to worry
about there, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『魔王』か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Demon King...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>読んだ本には、
そう書いてあったぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's how all the books
I read refer to him.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんたちは
『魔王』を倒した
『英雄』だって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When Mister &lt;Cless&gt; and company
defeated the "Demon King"
they became "Heroes."</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>確かに彼は
多くの人の命を奪った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, I've ended the lives
of many innocent beings.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『魔王』と呼ばれても
仕方がないのかもしれない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What I've done is no different
from the "Demon King."</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、それは
魔科学を排除する
ためだったんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You see, he was just trying
to stop Magitechnology.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔科学って
前に聞いたよな！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Magitechnology!? We've heard of
that before back with &lt;Klarth&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>世界のことわりを
破壊するって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's related to how the world
was almost destroyed, right...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278844</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、ダオスは、
魔科学を……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, Dhaos trying to
stop Magitechnology
makes no sense...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスは人間に魔科学を
やめるように言った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos only ever wanted humans
to stop abusing Magitechnology.
He knew of its dangers.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それでもその利便性を
追求する人間たちは、
魔科学をやめなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, due to the selfish interests of people,
Magitechnology research continued.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、ダオスは
人々を襲った……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then Dhaos attacked the humans...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>未だその真実は
語られないままだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is because people refused to listen
to him. They would rather wage war
than listen to an honest plea.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちがそのことを
知らないように</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That part was concealed from history.
You wouldn't have known. Mankind's
ego wouldn't let it BE known.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>自分たちがおかした罪の重さに
誰も向き合うことができないまま、
世界は前に進んでいっている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've killed and sinned. However, since it
was in everyone's best interests, the world
moved on and ignored our—my crimes. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279536</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたし、魔術を
暴走させてしまったんです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mister &lt;Cless&gt;...It's my fault that
magic has gone rampant...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279536</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それがもしかしたら、
マナをたくさん使ってて、
それでダオスがわたしを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Prism Ring is consuming mana...and will
destroy the world eventually. If so, then Dhaos
thinks I'm a threat to the world, too... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279620</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、あれは
わざとと違うだろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, but that's completely wrong!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わざとじゃなくても
魔術使ったのは、
わたしだもん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's not wrong. All this happened
because I used magic...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……なるほどね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Is that so?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、君は
ダオスのされるがまま
なのかい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, Dhaos did leave
you be, didn't he?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279968</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……他に罪を償う方法が
ないなら、そうしたかも
しれないです……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...If that's not the "sin" he
was referring to, I'm not
sure what it could be...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうならないよう
ちゃんと方法見つけただろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There's nothing like that. I think you're
overthinking it way too much.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280132</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかってるってば</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I know, I know.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……誰が悪いとかいいとか、
人はすぐ決めたがる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>..."If there's evil in this world,
it lurks in the hearts of men."</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、何が罪で何が正義か、
それを決めるのは
自分の心じゃないかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>However, what is sinful and what
is just isn't something simply
determined by the heart.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>自分の心？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't determined...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>自分が自分の行動を
恥じるか、誇るか……
ってことですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>People decide what's good or
bad depending on what they're 
proud or ashamed of...correct?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……かな。
僕はダオスを倒したことを
後悔はしていない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Indeed. I used to have
no regrets inside of me
for defeating Dhaos.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも今でも思うんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...I'm not so sure now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスは滅ぼうとしていた
自分の故郷の世界樹を
生き返らせるため、戦っていた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos brought war and despair,
but he fought to bring his
homeworld back to life.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>自分の世界を守ろうとした彼を
倒した僕たちこそが、
実は悪だったんじゃないかって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We were both fighting to protect our
own worlds. In the end, it wasn't evil
what drove him. We were the same.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's not true! He was attacking
innocent people without any hesitation!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなことはないって、
いつも自分に言い聞かせてる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It wasn't. At every turn
he tried to talk to us.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、この世には多くの人がいて、
善悪の基準もその人の数だけある</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...people's standard of what's "good"
as well as their values differed.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いまだに僕は
自分のやったことに
答えを出せないでいる……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even now, I still can't tell what would have
been the right answer for that conflict...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それなのに、
『英雄』だなんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And yet, I'm labeled a "hero."...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_020_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……さあ、
話はこれくらいにして</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Okay, I believe that's enough
talk for one night.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>46</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281384</PointerOffset>
